00:15:26.740 --> 00:15:31.060
Yes, so, by singing along,
Lomax was doing something

00:15:31.060 --> 00:15:35.120
that he did throughout his career,
which was breaking down the barrier

00:15:35.120 --> 00:15:37.890
between professional
musician and amateur,

00:15:37.890 --> 00:15:39.550
saying that we're all musicians.

00:15:39.550 --> 00:15:40.850
We should all participate.

00:15:40.850 --> 00:15:44.890
And in fact, the singalongs are
one of many devices that he used

00:15:44.890 --> 00:15:48.400
to convince children and
general audiences listening in,

00:15:48.400 --> 00:15:50.840
on the Folk Music of
America broadcast,

00:15:50.840 --> 00:15:54.030
that they too were
contributors to American music

00:15:54.030 --> 00:15:56.560
and its cultural history.

00:15:56.560 --> 00:15:59.140
At the end of every program,

