00:29:51.370 --> 00:29:55.450
&gt;&gt; Tell us a little about yourself.

00:29:55.450 --> 00:29:56.750
&gt;&gt; Lawrence Davies: Okay.

00:29:56.750 --> 00:30:01.540
I'm just finishing up my PhD
