00:30:06.340 --> 00:30:14.730
Some of my work then was on
Alan Lomax and his radio career,

00:30:14.730 --> 00:30:18.530
but also how Alan Lomax
presented in particular,

00:30:18.530 --> 00:30:22.820
African American folksong
and blues and jazz,

00:30:22.820 --> 00:30:25.070
both in America and in Britain.

00:30:25.070 --> 00:30:29.970
And one of the things that
