00:31:54.990 --> 00:31:59.300
So. The Art of the Negro, is really
a series that Lomax write not long

00:31:59.300 --> 00:32:02.820
after his arrival in
Britain in 1951.

00:32:02.820 --> 00:32:06.620
And although, much of Lomax's
