00:32:31.370 --> 00:32:36.080
but also how these programs were
used to challenge the status quo,

00:32:36.080 --> 00:32:39.570
such as it was in the
1950s, about attitudes

00:32:39.570 --> 00:32:44.050
to the broader cultural value of
African-American music and culture.

00:32:44.050 --> 00:32:47.870
And I should also say at this
